data.title: Isabelle Marguerite Alix Félicie Marie de LIEDEKERKE (1914
data.meta_description: Isabelle Marguerite Alix Félicie Marie de LIEDEKERKE was born on September  7, 1914 in Bruxelles, 21004, Région Bruxelles-Capitale, Belgique, daughter of 'Charles' Honoré Elie Marie Joseph de LIEDEKERKE and Anne Marie Joséphine Françoise d'AUDIFFRET-PASQUIER. She was married on September 22, 1936 in Leefdaal, 24061, Vlaams-Brabant, Belgique to Philippe Evrard de LIMBURG STIRUM, they had 7 children. She died on May 30, 2004 in Bertem, 24009, Vlaams-Brabant, Belgique. This information is part of Arbre de Didier Van Lerberghe by Didier Van Lerberghe on Genealogy Online.
